## MCP-first (read-only)

| Need | Server |
|------|--------|
| Work items, pipelines, wiki | Azure DevOps MCP — org `<ADO-ORG>`, project `<ADO-PROJECT>` |
| Azure resources | Azure MCP with `--read-only` |

See `<ai-tooling-config>/.github/instructions/global-mcp.instructions.md`.

## Operating rules

1. Plan non-trivial changes in `docs/change-YYYY-MM-DD-*.md` first.
2. Wiki Mermaid: `::: mermaid` … `:::` (ADO syntax).
3. No secrets in git; no autonomous apply/deploy/commit.
4. Cross-repo changes: publish a change map (repos, order, rollback).

## Environments

`dev` → `tst` → `acc` → `prod` — tfvars and ADO environment names documented in wiki.
